Package: procapture
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ffmpeg
Description: Lightweight hardware-accelerated screen recorder
 ProCapture is a blazing-fast, lightweight screen recorder for Linux.
 Built natively with C and GTK3, it leverages your GPU for hardware-accelerated
 recording with near-zero CPU overhead.